    "• The chain-of-thought (CoT) The CoT is a few-shot prompting technology (also known as in-context learning, ICL) proposed by Google (Wei et al. 2022b) to help large language models better understand language requests by providing contextual information.",
    "It can improve the model's accuracy and flexibility, enhancing its processing capability.",
